Package: rangeos-core
Version: 0.2.31
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: RangeOS AI Project <ops@rangeos.ai>
Depends: python3.12, python3-pip, python3-venv, postgresql, redis-server, libvirt-daemon-system
Recommends: rangeos-system, rangeos-assets
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: RangeOS AI Backend Microservice Core
 Installs and configures the full RangeOS AI microservice mesh including
 lab-service, orchestration-service, forensics-service, reporting-service,
 ai-service, policy-service, identity-service, telemetry-service,
 api-gateway, search-service, and update-service.
 .
 Python virtualenvs are created per-service. PostgreSQL databases and
 Redis channels are provisioned during post-install.
